nursing interventions for men electing for watchful waiting as an alternative to 
treatment for prostate cancer, including patient teaching and support services. 
Future study should examine the role of nurses in managing uncertainty, 
especially in patient teaching and in the development, implementation and 
evaluation of interventions to manage uncertainty.

